Rogue
Focused on agility and light combat, rogues are specialised on Light Armour and Melee Weapons.
In addition, Handguns, Melee, and SMGs are the preferred weapons, and a light hacking skill-set makes for a versatile combatant.
Specialist
Focused and highly skilled in technical knowledge. Specialists are well adapted to Hacking and Crafting.
Handguns and Snipers are the preferred weapons for Specialists.
Enforcer
Focused on Heavy combat doctrine. Enforcers prefer the usage of Heavy Weaponry and Armoury.
Their training makes them well suited for Hand-To-Hand combat if the situation arises.